<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About - Poké Weakness Finder</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.6/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-4Q6Gf2aSP4eDXB8Miphtr37CMZZQ5oXLH2yaXMJ2w8e2ZtHTl7GptT4jmndRuHDT" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/style2.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&family=Press+Start+2P&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/pokeball.png" type="image/x-icon">
</head>

<body>
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg pokemon-navbar" aria-label="Main Navigation">
        <div class="container-fluid container-max-width">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">
                <img src="/images/pokeball.png" alt="Pokedex Logo" class="navbar-logo">
                Poké Weakness Finder
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav"
                aria-controls="navbarNav" aria-expanded="false" aria-label="Toggle navigation">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link" aria-current="page" href="/">Home</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="nav-item">
                        <a class="nav-link active" href="/about">About</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container mt-5 about-content">
        <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
            <ol class="breadcrumb">
                <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="/">Home</a></li>
                <li class="breadcrumb-item active" aria-current="page">About</li>
            </ol>
        </nav>

        <div class="card about-card p-4">
            <h1 class="card-title text-center mb-4 about-title">About Poké Weakness Finder</h1>
            <p class="card-text lead text-center">
                Welcome to Poké Weakness Finder, your ultimate companion for discovering detailed information and
                weaknesses of all your favorite Pokémon!
            </p>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <h4>Our Mission</h4>
                    <p>
                        Our goal is to provide a comprehensive and user-friendly platform for Pokémon trainers and
                        enthusiasts to quickly find vital statistics, abilities, descriptions, and crucial type
                        weaknesses/resistances for any Pokémon. We believe that informed trainers are stronger trainers!
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mb-3">
                    <h4>Data Source</h4>
                    <p>
                        All Pokémon data on this website is sourced from the <a href="https://pokeapi.co/"
                            target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PokéAPI</a>, a free and open-source RESTful API
                        that provides access to a wealth of Pokémon information. We extend our gratitude to the PokéAPI
                        community for their invaluable resource.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                    <h4>How to Use</h4>
                    <ul class="list-unstyled text-start mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
                        <li><i class="bi bi-search me-2 text-primary"></i>Use the search bar on the Home page to find
                            Pokémon by name or Pokedex ID.</li>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-card-checklist me-2 text-success"></i>Click on a search result to view
                            detailed information including base stats, types, and a full description.</li>
                        <li><i class="bi bi-shield-fill-exclamation me-2 text-warning"></i>Easily identify Pokémon
                            weaknesses and resistances to strategize your battles!</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-12 text-center">
                    <h4>Source Code</h4>
                    <p>
                        This project is open-source! You can explore the full codebase and contribute on GitHub:
                    </p>
                    <a href="https://github.com/miramsalp/poke-weakness-finder" target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-dark github-btn">
                        <i class="bi bi-github me-2"></i>View on GitHub
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <hr class="my-4">
            <div class="text-center">
                <p class="text-muted">Developed with ❤️ for Pokémon fans everywhere.</p>
                <a href="/" class="btn btn-primary mt-3">Back to Home</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
